# Schola

Malaysian career exploration platform for students aged 13–19 (Form 1 through SPM leavers).

**Website:** schola.org.my  
**Languages:** English and Bahasa Malaysia (bilingual)  
**Social media:** Instagram (@schola.my), TikTok

## Products & Tools

- **Job guides** — bilingual career information pages covering salary, education pathways, demand, and expert interviews. Used as the knowledge source for [[entities/Ola]].
- **[[entities/Ola]]** — AI chatbot assistant embedded on the website for student career exploration
- **[[concepts/Social-Media-Comment-Classification-Pipeline]]** — internal AI automation pipeline for analysing engagement on social posts

